farmersdelight.advancement.craft_knife=Plunder n' Pillage
farmersdelight.advancement.craft_knife.desc=Make yerself a Dagger ta plunder more bounty from plant an' animal alike
farmersdelight.advancement.eat_comfort_food=Warm an' Cozy!
farmersdelight.advancement.eat_comfort_food.desc=Eat a bowl's worth, an' get yerself healin' up steady, hunger be darned!
farmersdelight.advancement.eat_nourishing_food=Hearty an' Full!
farmersdelight.advancement.eat_nourishing_food.desc=Eat a plate's worth, an' be free o' hunger or fatigue fer a good while!
farmersdelight.advancement.get_fd_seed=Crops o' the Wild
farmersdelight.advancement.get_fd_seed.desc=Rumours sing o' four veggies growin' wild in many lands... but ye bet they got 'em in booty somewhere!
farmersdelight.advancement.get_ham=Ye Old Chop Chop
farmersdelight.advancement.get_ham.desc=Slay them hogs or hoglins wit' yer dagger ta get a juicy cut o' Hog's Leg!
farmersdelight.advancement.get_mushroom_colony=Not Mushroom Left!
farmersdelight.advancement.get_mushroom_colony.desc=Shear up a shroom infestation. Harr, they only grow this crazy in some real rich filth...
farmersdelight.advancement.get_rich_soil=Plant Grub
farmersdelight.advancement.get_rich_soil.desc=Piles o' Garbage turn inta Rich Filth... hmph! Ain't no pirate gon' need ta improve no farm!
farmersdelight.advancement.harvest_ropelogged_tomato=To tha Crow's Nest!
farmersdelight.advancement.harvest_ropelogged_tomato.desc=Yer tomato vines be mighty skilled at climbin' rope o'er them, so get ta hangin'!
farmersdelight.advancement.harvest_straw=Weavin' Rigging
farmersdelight.advancement.harvest_straw.desc=Stab them grasses, wheats or rices, ta gather fiber fer yer sail rig
farmersdelight.advancement.hit_raider_with_rotten_tomato=To tha plank wit' ye!
farmersdelight.advancement.hit_raider_with_rotten_tomato.desc=Show them raiders yer mettle... with a rottin' tomato?
farmersdelight.advancement.master_chef=Grand Frigate's Cook
farmersdelight.advancement.master_chef.desc=Have a taste o' every grub ye can get yer hook on!
farmersdelight.advancement.obtain_netherite_knife=If Ye Dive Too Deep...
farmersdelight.advancement.obtain_netherite_knife.desc=Ye might just get yer dagger decked in Blackbeard's Alloy! But beware, lest ye incur his wrath...
farmersdelight.advancement.place_campfire=Bonfire Lit
farmersdelight.advancement.place_campfire.desc=Warm yerself an' yer food around a Campfire
farmersdelight.advancement.place_cooking_pot=Come Eat, Ye Scallywags!
farmersdelight.advancement.place_cooking_pot.desc=Heat up a pot and get ta cookin' up some grub!
farmersdelight.advancement.place_feast=Captain's Treat
farmersdelight.advancement.place_feast.desc=Aye, some grubs be big enough ta put down an' serve a whole crew!
farmersdelight.advancement.place_organic_compost=Stinkin' ol' Landlubbin'!
farmersdelight.advancement.place_organic_compost.desc=Put down sum Piles o' Garbage. Ward off the stench quicker wit' sun, bilgewater an' shrooms!
farmersdelight.advancement.place_skillet=Scaldin' Irons!
farmersdelight.advancement.place_skillet.desc=Tired o' wieldin' yer skillet? Crouch an' plop it down!
farmersdelight.advancement.plant_all_crops=Landlubber's Bounty
farmersdelight.advancement.plant_all_crops.desc=Sow them foodie plants o' all kinds: veggies, 'shrooms, tubers an' fruits!
farmersdelight.advancement.plant_rice=Soggy Weeds
farmersdelight.advancement.plant_rice.desc=Plant a buncha Rice grains in a puddle o' bilgewater
farmersdelight.advancement.root=Farmer's Delight
farmersdelight.advancement.root.desc=A great sea o' flavor awaits ye!
farmersdelight.advancement.use_cutting_board=Keep Yer Gaff Steady
farmersdelight.advancement.use_cutting_board.desc=Wield yer tool o' choice, an' chop up a thing in the Choppin' Block
farmersdelight.advancement.use_skillet=Fryin' Over Yonder
farmersdelight.advancement.use_skillet.desc=Bring ye ol' Skillet ta cook in long trips. Wield yer grub an' heat 'em up!
