farmersdelight.jei.info.dough=Ta mix some Raw Hard Tack, ye can drench some Wheat in a Pail o' Bilge. Fer some reason, the bilge never goes down...
farmersdelight.jei.info.ham=Hogs an' Hoglins will give ye this fine meat cut, so long as yer cuttin' tool's light enough.
farmersdelight.jei.info.knife=Daggers make fer a quick slashin'!\n\nSlay a beast ta always get a piece o' its other drops, or chop grasses an' wheats ta get Fiber.
farmersdelight.jei.info.straw=Dry an' firm, good fer makin' ropes. Run yer dagger by them grasses, both crop an' wild, ta get some.
farmersdelight.jei.info.wild_beetroots=Bloody Potatoes can be spotted sproutin' around port, by the sea shore.
farmersdelight.jei.info.wild_cabbages=Leafers can be spotted sproutin' around port, by the sea shore.
farmersdelight.jei.info.wild_carrots=Orange Weeds can be spotted sproutin' in mild land. Set sail ta forests n' plains!
farmersdelight.jei.info.wild_onions=Stink Bulbs can be spotted sproutin' in mild land. Set sail ta forests n' plains!
farmersdelight.jei.info.wild_potatoes=Taters can be spotted sproutin' in frigid land. Set sail ta mountains n' taigas!
farmersdelight.jei.info.wild_rice=Rice weeds can be spotted swimmin' by the shallow waters o' swamps n' jungles.
farmersdelight.jei.info.wild_tomatoes=Tomatoes can be spotted sproutin' in hot, hot land. Set sail ta deserts n' savannas!
